creator: Mana.ai
descriptionHtml:
Spend your time better. Mana helps you reach your fullest potential with the easiest time management tool to achieve your goals! Our experts on every time management methodology you can think of are focused on helping you to effectively create more time value in your life. Realizing your dreams requires understanding your priorities. No matter who you are, there are only 24 hours in a day: 168 per week. We help you use them better.

WHAT MAKES US DIFFERENT:
1. We enable holistic reflection
Mana is the only self-care and goal-setting system that reveals the whole picture.
We show how you spend your time - 24/7, providing you with accurate data you can use to make changes for the better.

2. We offer full transparency into all of your time
Use Mana’s beautiful interface and machine-learning powered suggestions to log your time. Integrations with apps you already use make pen & paper journaling and complex calculations a thing of the past.

3. We empower you
We help you understand your unique values and encourage you with support and accountability to spend more time on the things you value and less on the things you don’t.

WHAT YOU’LL GET:
- World’s easiest tool for tracking how you spend all of your time
- Goal setting system to help you set resolutions and see your progress
- Reflection journal for staying mindful about your wellbeing, progress, and goals
- Personalized expert guidance that empowers you to create time value for yourself
